== 0. Files

README		this file
Makefile	Makefile for libCSCSupervisor.so
Makefile.rules	Definitions to compile this package outside of TriDAS tree
include/	include files for CSCSupervisor and EmuApplication
src/common/	source files for CSCSupervisor and EmuApplication
test/		files to test applications
   config.xml	XDAQ XML configuration file to run everyone on localhost
   bootxdaq	XDAQ executive boot shell script
   EmuFED/	dummy EmuFEDCrate application
   EmuPC/	dummy EmuPeripheralCrate application
   EmuDAQ/	dummy EmuDAQManager application

== 1. CVS access

foo> cd ~/work
foo> export CVSROOT=:pserver:anonymous@cmscvs.cern.ch:/cvs_server/repositories/TriDAS
foo> cvs login
...
foo> cvs co -r Release-1_4 -d cscSV TriDAS/emu/cscSV

== 2. Build and run

foo> cd cscSV
foo> export XDAQ_ROOT=/home/foo/work/tridas
foo> make install
foo> test/bootxdaq start

